web_snippets: Matt Nagin is not your average comedian. His unique blend of observational humor, biting satire, and absurdity has audiences rolling in the aisles.
Matt Nagin is a writer, educator, actor, filmmaker, and standup comedian. Matt has taught college writing at six different institutions in the NYC area.
Matt Nagin is an author and comedian who has published four books, acted in numerous film and TV projects, and performed standup in seven countries.
